  "instructions": [
    "preheat oven to 425 degrees fahrenheit.",
    "in a large bowl combine chopped onion, bell pepper, carrots, zucchini, and fennel.",
    "drizzle with olive oil and toss to coat.",
    "spread the vegetable mixture on a baking sheet and roast for 30 minutes.",
    "add the kimchi to the baking sheet and continue to roast for an additional 10 minutes.",
    "meanwhile toast the baguette cubes in the oven for 5-7 minutes or until crispy.",
    "assemble the tagine by placing the roasted vegetables on a serving platter and topping with crispy bread and kimchi.",
    "season with salt to taste."
